## 3. CCNA Exam Guide & Mnemonics

* **Top-to-Bottom Mnemonic (7 to 1):** * **A**ll **P**eople **S**eem **T**o **N**eed **D**ata **P**rocessing
* **Bottom-to-Top Mnemonic (1 to 7):** * **P**lease **D**o **N**ot **T**hrow **S**ausage **P**izza **A**way
* **Troubleshooting Paradigm:** * Always troubleshoot systematically. Start at Layer 1 (Verify physical cabling and link lights), move to Layer 2 (Check MAC learning and VLAN alignment), and then proceed to Layer 3 (Verify IP configuration and test ping to the default gateway).
